  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0da9\u0dcf\u0dc0:\u0dbd\u0ddd\u0d9a \u0dc1\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dad\u0dcf \u0db6\u0ddc\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0d82 \u0dad\u0dbb\u0d9c\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dba\u0da7 \u0dc3\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dc3\u0dd4\u0d9a\u0db8\u0dca \u0dbd\u0dd0\u0db6\u0dd6 '\u0dc0\u0dc0\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dda \u0dc3\u0da7\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc1\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba'",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sports: 'Vavuniya Sutton Shuriya' qualified for the World Boxing Championship",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sevmini Imesha Jayawardena, who lives in Vavuniya, Malmaduwa village, managed to participate in the World Championship 'Kickboxing' tournament to be held in London next August.",
        "She told the BBC that although she lives in a very difficult area, she will not give up on her goal even though some people say that boxing is not suitable for girls.",
        "To qualify for the World Championship, she recently won a gold medal in the qualifying competition held in Chennai, India."
      ],
